;handles all evolution logic for the cells

;evolution runs every 50 ticks (50 ticks = 1 generation) 
;looks at which agents performed best and creates new generation by combining their genomes (recombination)
;and adding small random changes (mutation) 

;FITNESS SCORES:
; macrophages: eat-count + (ticks-survived * 0.1)
; neutrophils: bacteria-killed - (friendly-fire * 0.5)
; bacteria: ticks-survived + (times-fooled * 2)


